				<wikidot:authorName>TyGently</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>2038009</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <blockquote> <p>Can't you see the sky is not the limit no more?<br /> I can see the elevator crash through the floor<br /> I can still see yesterday sailing away<br /> Seven billion people who got nothing to say<br /> <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ZKsQuZVxPnc">Are you coming on to me?</a></p> </blockquote> <p>Thanks to consistent collaborators Taffeta, GreenWolf, Jacob Conwell, and A Random Day for help and support with this undertaking. Image was created entirely by me, font used is Roboto Mono.</p> <p>I'm now pleased to include Jacob Conwell's excellent <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/end-of-an-era">End of an Era</a> as an interlude, written to chronicle the drama in Site 64 occurring parallel to Comedown Machine's Intermission and second act. I didn't even ask him to do this, he did it on his own because he's just that cool.</p> 
				 	]]>
